metadata.title: VIFAH V98SET3 Outdoor Wood 5-Piece Dining Set
features: FSC High Density Eucalyptus (Shorea) is pre-treated, expertly kiln-dried, extremely durable for outdoor/indoor use
FSC High Density Eucalyptus (Shorea) is mold, mildew, fungi, termites, rot and decay resistant
FSC High Density Eucalyptus (Shorea) is and harvested from protected forests
description: Make way for dinner parties, idle summer cocktails, and the optimization of fresh breezes to come with this Malibu Outdoor Patio 5-piece Wood Dining Set! Made from 100% Eucalyptus - a very durable Hardwood, this set that can stand up to all kinds of changes in the weather. The cores of the Eucalyptus is very dense; thereby it is weather-resistant. Comes in the beautiful Natural Wood Finish, this set will be a great addition to your outdoor patio!
